    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-01-04</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-01-18T15:58:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Legislative Branch Appropriations Act, 1987 to allow the Clerk of the House of Representatives, at the request of a Member of the House, to donate computers and related peripheral tools previously used by the Member to a public elementary or secondary school designated by such Member without regard to whether the donation: (1) is a cost to the government; or (2) has a recoverable value. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To permit members of the House of Representatives to donate used computer equipment to public elementary and secondary schools designated by the members.</title>
